I"<div class="p">With quick perception, trained with skill,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The mind assails the truth;</div>
<div class="p">The lighted fuse compels the core</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To see the ways of sooth.</div>
<div class="p">And merry in the fettle light,</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; And sprightly in the ways</div>
<div class="p">Of noble cause, the truth itself</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Invites the passing gaze.</div>
<div class="p">And gamboling in innocence</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The truth at Eden's gate</div>
<div class="p">Calls out the name of passersby</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; And gently bids them 'Wait!'</div>
<div class="p">But men go on, too bored to stay</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; To listen to the call</div>
<div class="p">That sweetly warbles in their path</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; And threatens to enthrall.</div>
